gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 120, Trail Blazers 108
gameRecap.excerpt: Nikola Jokic put up 27 points, 22 rebounds and 12 assists for the Nuggets as they defeated the Trail Blazers, 120-108. This is Jokics 15th triple-double of the season and 120th of his career. Jamal Murray added 13 points, nine rebounds and 10 assists in the victory, while Scoot Henderson tallied 30 points and five rebounds for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort, the 2nd 30+ point game of his career. The Nuggets improve to 34-16 on the season, while the Trail Blazers fall to 15-34.
